.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-SUMMARY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-summary \- aggregate invoice counts and total received
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-summary
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns counts of paid, unpaid, and expired invoices and the total
amount received across all paid invoices.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{total, paid, unpaid, expired, total_received_msat}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-list (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-list-paid (1)
